#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Konfigurator: &krusader;'s Configuration Center"
msgstr "Konfigurator: &krusader;-jevo središče za konfiguracijo"

#. Tag: primary
#: konfigurator.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj"

#. Tag: secondary
#: konfigurator.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Krusader"
msgstr "Krusader"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Konfigurator is &krusader;s configuration center. When running &krusader;, "
"use <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"&krusader;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, and it will start Konfigurator. "
"There you can modify the way &krusader; works and customize it to your own "
"needs. At any time, pressing the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button applies "
"the changes, pressing <guibutton>Close</guibutton> closes Konfigurator, and "
"pressing <guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> re-applies &krusader;'s "
"<quote>factory</quote> settings. Konfigurator is divided into pages, each "
"containing items related to that page. For some changes to the &GUI;, you "
"have to close and restart &krusader;."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurator je &krusader;-jev konfiguracijski center. Ko izvajate "
"&krusader;, uporabite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &krusader;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in "
"zagnal bo Konfigurator. Tam lahko spremenite način &krusader; deluje in ga "
"prilagodite svojim potrebam. Kadar koli pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Uporabi</"
"guibutton>, uveljavite spremembe, pritisnete <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>, "
"da zaprete konfigurator, in pritisnete <guibutton>Privzeto</guibutton>, da "
"ponovno uveljavi &krusader;-jev <quote >tovarniške</quote> nastavitve. "
"Konfigurator je razdeljen na strani, od katerih vsaka vsebuje elemente, "
"povezane s to stranjo. Za nekatere spremembe &GUI;, morate zapreti in znova "
"zagnati &krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &krusader;-1.80.0 the <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">Key-Bindings</"
"link> and <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Main Toolbar</link>-<link linkend="
"\"actions_toolbar\">Actions Toolbar</link> have received their own "
"configuration windows and so they are not a part anymore of Konfigurator, "
"you can configure them now via the <link linkend=\"settings-menu"
"\"><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"Od &krusader;-1.80.0 naprej <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">Vezi tipk</link> "
"in <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Glavna orodna vrstica</link>-<link linkend="
"\"actions_toolbar\">Orodna vrstica za dejanja</link> so prejeli lastna "
"konfiguracijska okna in tako niso več del Konfiguratorja, zdaj jih lahko "
"konfigurirate prek menija <link linkend=\"settings-menu"
"\"><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu></link> ."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup"
msgstr "Začeti"

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Startup configuration</title>"
msgstr "<title>Konfiguracija zagona</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: konfigurator.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Startup configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija zagona</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The startup page determines the way that &krusader; looks (and works) when "
"it is launched. It is divided into two main parts:"
msgstr ""
"Začetna stran določa način, kako &krusader; izgleda (in deluje), ko se "
"zažene. Razdeljen je na dva glavna dela:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:55 konfigurator.docbook:356 konfigurator.docbook:616
#: konfigurator.docbook:804 konfigurator.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>General</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Startup Profile</guilabel>: Starts the selected <link linkend="
"\"panel_profiles\">Panel profile</link> at startup. <guilabel>&lt;Last "
"session&gt;</guilabel> is a special Panel Profile, it is saved automatically "
"when closing &krusader;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zagonski profil</guilabel>: Zažene izbrani <link linkend="
"\"panel_profiles\">Profil plošče</link> ob zagonu. <guilabel>&lt;Zadnja "
"seja&gt;</guilabel> je poseben profil plošče, ki se samodejno shrani, ko "
"zaprete &krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show splashscreen</guilabel>: Displays a splash screen when "
"starting &krusader;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži pozdravni zaslon</guilabel>: prikaže pozdravni zaslon ob "
"zagonu &krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Single Instance Mode</guilabel>: Allows only one &krusader; "
"instance to run."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Način enega primerka</guilabel>: dovoljuje samo en &krusader; "
"primerek za zagon."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Fallback Icon Theme</guilabel>: Allows you to configure a fallback "
"icon theme for &krusader;. Whenever icon is not found in system icon theme, "
"this theme will be used as a fallback. If the fallback theme does not "
"contain the icon, Breeze or Oxygen will be used if any of these are present."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Tema nadomestne ikone</guilabel>: Omogoča vam konfiguracijo teme "
"nadomestne ikone za &krusader;. Kadarkoli ikona ni najdena v temi sistemske "
"ikone, bo ta tema uporabljena kot nadomestna. Če nadomestna tema ne vsebuje "
"ikone, bo uporabljena Breeze ali Oxygen, če je katera od teh prisotna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Interface"
msgstr "Uporabniški vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determines which parts of the user interface are visible after start-up."
msgstr "Določa, kateri deli uporabniškega vmesnika so vidni po zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Save last position, size and panel settings</guilabel>: When "
"launched, &krusader; resizes itself to the size it was when last shut-down. "
"&krusader; also appears in the same location on the screen, having panels "
"sorted and aligned as they were. If this option is unchecked, you can use "
"the menu <menuchoice> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Position</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> option to manually set &krusader; size and "
"position at start-up."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Shrani zadnji položaj, velikost in nastavitve plošče</guilabel>: "
"Ko se zažene, &krusader; spremeni velikost na velikost, kakršna je bila ob "
"zadnji zaustavitvi. &krusader; se prikaže tudi na istem mestu na zaslonu, "
"plošče pa so razvrščene in poravnane, kot so bile. Če ta možnost ni "
"potrjena, lahko uporabite možnost menija <menuchoice> <guimenu>Okno</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani položaj</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> za ročno "
"nastavitev &krusader; velikost in položaj ob zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Update default panel settings</guilabel>: If checked, the default "
"panel settings will be updated after start-up."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Posodobi privzete nastavitve plošče</guilabel>: Če je označeno, "
"bodo privzete nastavitve plošče posodobljene po zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Start to system tray</guilabel>: if checked, &krusader; starts to "
"tray (if minimize to tray is set), without showing the main window."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Začni v sistemsko vrstico</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; "
"zažene v pladnju (če je nastavljeno minimiziranje na pladenj), ne da bi "
"prikazal glavno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Save component settings on exit</guilabel>: If checked, restores "
"the user interface components to their condition when last shut-down."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Shrani nastavitve komponente ob izhodu</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"povrne komponente uporabniškega vmesnika v njihovo stanje ob zadnji "
"zaustavitvi."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show function keys</guilabel>: If checked, the <link linkend="
"\"fnkeys\">FN Keys Bar</link> is visible after start-up."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži funkcijske tipke</guilabel>: Če je označeno, je <link "
"linkend=\"fnkeys\">vrstica s tipkami FN</link> vidna po zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show statusbar</guilabel>: If checked, the <link linkend="
"\"mainwindow\">Statusbar</link> is visible after start-up. Available only if "
"the <guilabel>Save component settings on exit</guilabel> item is unchecked."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži vrstico stanja</guilabel>: Če je označeno, je <link linkend="
"\"mainwindow\">vrstica stanja</link> vidna po zagonu. Na voljo samo, če "
"element <guilabel>Shrani nastavitve komponente ob izhodu</guilabel> ni "
"označen."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show command line</guilabel>: If checked, the <link linkend="
"\"cmdline\">Command Line</link> is visible after start-up. Available only if "
"the <guilabel>Save component settings on exit</guilabel> item is unchecked."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži ukazno vrstico</guilabel>: če je označeno, je <link linkend="
"\"cmdline\">ukazna vrstica</link> vidna po zagonu. Na voljo samo, če element "
"<guilabel>Shrani nastavitve komponente ob izhodu</guilabel> ni označen."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show embedded terminal</guilabel>: If checked, the <link linkend="
"\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> is visible after start-up. Available "
"only if the <guilabel>Save component settings on exit</guilabel> item is "
"unchecked."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži vdelan terminal</guilabel>: če je označeno, je <link "
"linkend=\"termemu\">terminalni emulator</link> viden po zagonu. Na voljo "
"samo, če element <guilabel>Shrani nastavitve komponente ob izhodu</guilabel> "
"ni označen."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panel"
msgstr "Plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can determine the look and feel of panel - which means finetuning "
"the application to your needs. The page is divided into six tabs: "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel>, <guilabel>View</guilabel>, <guilabel>Buttons</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Selection Mode</guilabel>, <guilabel>Media Menu</"
"guilabel>, and <guilabel>Layout</guilabel>:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite videz in občutek plošče - kar pomeni natančno "
"prilagajanje aplikacije vašim potrebam. Stran je razdeljena na šest "
"zavihkov: <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>, <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Gumbi</guilabel>, <guilabel>Izbirni način</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Medijski meni </guilabel> in <guilabel>Postavitev</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:178 konfigurator.docbook:1026 konfigurator.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošno</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigator bar"
msgstr "Navigacijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Edit Mode by default</guilabel>: If checked, show editable path in "
"Navigator bar by default."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeti način urejanja</guilabel>: Če je označeno, privzeto "
"pokaži pot, ki jo je mogoče urejati, v vrstici Krmarja."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show full path by default</guilabel>: If checked, always show full "
"path in Navigator bar by default."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeto pokaži celotno pot</guilabel>: Če je označeno, vedno "
"privzeto pokaži celotno pot v vrstici Krmarja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operation"
msgstr "Operacija"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Autoselect Folders</guilabel>: When <link linkend=\"edit-menu"
"\">you select a group of files</link> (either by using <guilabel>Select "
"Group</guilabel> or by using <guilabel>Select All</guilabel>), &krusader; "
"checks this option. If checked, the folders matching the select criteria are "
"also selected. Otherwise, only files are selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samodejno izberi mape</guilabel>: Ko <link linkend=\"edit-menu"
"\">izberete skupino datotek</link> (bodisi z uporabo <guilabel>Izberi "
"skupino</guilabel> ali z uporabo <guilabel> Izberi vse</guilabel>), "
"&krusader; preveri to možnost. Če je označeno, so izbrane tudi mape, ki "
"ustrezajo kriterijem izbire. V nasprotnem primeru so izbrane samo datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Rename selects extension</guilabel>: When <link linkend=\"renaming"
"\">you rename a file</link>, the whole text is selected. If you want "
"<trademark class=\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark> like renaming of "
"just the name, without extension, deselect this item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preimenuj izbere razširitev</guilabel>: Ko <link linkend=\"renaming"
"\">preimenuješ datoteko</link>, je izbrano celotno besedilo. Če želite, da "
"<trademark class=\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark> preimenuje samo "
"ime, brez razširitve, prekličite izbiro tega elementa."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Unselect files before copy/move</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; "
"remove the selection marks from files or folders before <link linkend="
"\"copying\">copying or moving</link> them to the new location."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prekliči izbiro datotek pred kopiranjem/premikanjem</guilabel>: če "
"je označeno, &krusader; odstranite izbirne oznake iz datotek ali map, preden "
"jih <link linkend=\"copying\">kopirate ali premaknete</link> na novo "
"lokacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Filter dialog remembers settings</guilabel>: If checked, the "
"filter dialog will be opened with the last filter settings that where "
"applied to the panel."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pogovorno okno filtra si zapomni nastavitve</guilabel>: Če je "
"označeno, se bo pogovorno okno filtra odprlo z zadnjimi nastavitvami filtra, "
"ki so bile uporabljene na plošči."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabs"
msgstr "Zavihki"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use fullpath tab names</guilabel>: If checked, display the full "
"path in the <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Folder tabs</link>; otherwise only "
"the last part of the path is displayed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabi imena zavihkov s polno potjo</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"prikaže celotno pot v <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">zavihkih map</link>; "
"drugače je prikazan samo zadnji del poti."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Expanding tabs</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; expands the "
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">folder tabs</link> to fill the whole bar."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razširjeni zavihki</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; razširi "
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">zavihke mape</link>, da zapolni celotno "
"vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Close tab by double click</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; "
"allows closing the <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">folder tabs</link> by "
"double-clicking on them."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zapri zavihek z dvojnim klikom</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"&krusader; omogoča zapiranje <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">zavihkov mape</"
"link> z dvojnim klikom nanje."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Insert tabs after current</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; "
"inserts new tabs to the right of the current one instead of placing them "
"into the end of the <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Tab bar</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vstavi zavihke za trenutnim</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; "
"vstavi nove zavihke desno od trenutnega, namesto da bi jih postavil na konec "
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">vrstice z zavihki</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Duplicate active tab by click</guilabel>: Lets you select the "
"active tab duplication mode (<guimenuitem>Disabled</guimenuitem> (no "
"clicking association), <guimenuitem>Alt+Click</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Ctrl+Click</guimenuitem>)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Podvoji aktivni zavihek s klikom</guilabel>: Omogoča izbiro načina "
"podvajanja aktivnega zavihka (<guimenuitem>Onemogočeno</guimenuitem> (brez "
"povezave s klikom), <guimenuitem>Alt+klik</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem> "
"Ctrl+klik</guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Tab Bar position</guilabel>: Lets you choose <link linkend="
"\"folder-tabs\">Tab bar</link> position (<guimenuitem>Bottom</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>Top</guimenuitem>)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Položaj vrstice z zavihki</guilabel>: omogoča izbiro položaja "
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">vrstice z zavihki</link> (<guimenuitem>Spodaj</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Zgoraj</guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show close tab buttons</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays "
"close buttons on <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">tabs</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži gumbe za zapiranje zavihkov</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"&krusader; prikaže gumbe za zapiranje na <link linkend=\"folder-tabs"
"\">zavihkih</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show new tab button</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays "
"new tab button on the <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Tab bar</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži gumb za nov zavihek</guilabel>: Če je označeno, &krusader; "
"prikaže gumb za nov zavihek v <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">vrstici z "
"zavihki</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show Tab Bar on single tab</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; "
"displays the Tab Bar even if there is only one <link linkend=\"folder-tabs"
"\">tab</link> on the panel."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži vrstico z zavihki na posameznem zavihku</guilabel>: Če je "
"označeno, &krusader; prikaže vrstico z zavihki, tudi če je na plošči samo en "
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">zavihek</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>New tab button duplicates a tab</guilabel>: If checked, new tab "
"button duplicates a <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">tab</link>, otherwise it "
"opens a tab in home folder."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Gumb Nov zavihek podvoji zavihek</guilabel>: Če je označeno, gumb "
"Nov zavihek podvoji <link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">zavihek</link>, sicer "
"odpre zavihek v domači mapi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search bar"
msgstr "Iskalna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Start by typing</guilabel>: allows to select if <link linkend="
"\"quicksearch\">quick search</link> feature is used. When checked, you can "
"open search bar and start searching by typing something while viewing folder "
"contents in the active panel."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Začnite s tipkanjem</guilabel>: omogoča izbiro, ali je uporabljena "
"funkcija <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">hitro iskanje</link>. Ko je označeno, "
"lahko odprete iskalno vrstico in začnete iskati tako, da nekaj vnesete, "
"medtem ko si ogledujete vsebino mape na aktivni plošči."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case sensitive</guilabel>: When you use the <link linkend="
"\"quicksearch\">search</link> or <link linkend=\"quickfilter\">filter</link> "
"feature: If checked (the &UNIX; default), all files beginning with capital "
"letters appear before files beginning with lower case letters; otherwise, "
"all files beginning with a specified letter (capital or otherwise) will be "
"displayed together."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami</guilabel>: Ko uporabljate "
"funkcijo <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">iskanje</link> ali <link linkend="
"\"quickfilter\">filter</link>: Če je označeno (privzeto za &UNIX; ), so vse "
"datoteke, ki se začnejo z velikimi črkami, prikazane pred datotekami, ki se "
"začnejo z malimi črkami; sicer bodo vse datoteke, ki se začnejo z določeno "
"črko (veliko ali drugo), prikazane skupaj."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Up/Down cancels search</guilabel>: Pressing &Up; or &Down; key "
"cancels <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">search</link> bar."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>gor/dol prekliče iskanje</guilabel>: pritisk &Up; ali &Down; tipka "
"prekliče vrstico <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">iskanje</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Folder navigation with Right Arrow</guilabel>: If checked, "
"pressing the &Right; key enters folder if no search text editing intention "
"is captured."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Krmarjenje po mapi s puščico desno</guilabel>: če je označeno, s "
"pritiskom tipke &Right; tipka vstopi v mapo, če ni zajet noben namen "
"urejanja iskalnega besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Position</guilabel>: Lets you choose <link linkend=\"quicksearch"
"\">search</link> and <link linkend=\"quickfilter\">filter</link> bar "
"position (<guimenuitem>Bottom</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Top</"
"guimenuitem>)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Položaj</guilabel>: Omogoča izbiro položaja vrstice <link linkend="
"\"quicksearch\">iskanje</link> in <link linkend=\"quickfilter\">filtra</"
"link> (<guimenuitem>Spodaj</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Zgoraj</"
"guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default mode</guilabel>: Lets you choose the search bar default "
"mode between <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">Search</link>, <guilabel>Select</"
"guilabel> and <link linkend=\"quickfilter\">Filter</link>. You can change "
"the mode later using the search bar itself."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeti način</guilabel>: omogoča izbiro privzetega načina "
"iskalne vrstice med <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">Iskanjem</link>, "
"<guilabel>Izberi</guilabel> in <link linkend=\"quickfilter\"> Filter</link>. "
"Način lahko pozneje spremenite s samo iskalno vrstico."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark Search"
msgstr "Iskanje po zaznamkih"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Always show search bar</guilabel>: If checked, make <link linkend="
"\"bookman\">bookmark search bar</link> always visible."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vedno pokaži iskalno vrstico</guilabel>: če je označeno, naj bo "
"<link linkend=\"bookman\">iskalna vrstica zaznamkov</link> vedno vidna."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Search in special items</guilabel>: If checked, <link linkend="
"\"bookman\">bookmark search</link> is also applied to special items in "
"bookmark menu like <guimenuitem>Trash</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Popular "
"&URL;s</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Jump Back</guimenuitem>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Išči v posebnih elementih</guilabel>: če je označeno, se <link "
"linkend=\"bookman\">iskanje po zaznamkih</link> uporablja tudi za posebne "
"elemente v meniju z zaznamki, kot je <guimenuitem>Smetnjak</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem >Priljubljeni &URL;</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Skoči nazaj</"
"guimenuitem> &etc;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status/Totalsbar"
msgstr "Stanje/skupna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show size in bytes too</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays "
"size in bytes on statusbar or totalsbar."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži tudi velikost v bajtih</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"&krusader; prikaže velikost v bajtih v vrstici stanja ali skupni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show space information</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays "
"free/total disk space in the Status-/Totalsbar."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži informacije o prostoru</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"&krusader; prikaže prosti/skupni prostor na disku v vrstici Stanje/skupna "
"vrstica."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr "Pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>View font</guilabel>: Allows you to change the font used inside "
"the file lists."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ogled pisave</guilabel>: Omogoča spreminjanje pisave, uporabljene "
"znotraj seznamov datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Tooltip delay (msec)</guilabel>: Allows you to configure the delay "
"in milliseconds between the moment you have stopped mouse pointer above an "
"item in a file list and the moment when the tooltip will be shown."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zamik orodja (msec)</guilabel>: Omogoča konfiguracijo zakasnitve v "
"milisekundah med trenutkom, ko ustavite kazalec miške nad elementom na "
"seznamu datotek, in trenutkom, ko se prikaže nasvet orodja."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use human readable file size</guilabel>: If checked, the file size "
"appears in kB, Mb &etc;, and not in bytes (default)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabi človeku berljivo velikost datoteke</guilabel>: Če je "
"označeno, se velikost datoteke prikaže v kB, Mb &etc; in ne v bajtih "
"(privzeto)."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Numeric permissions</guilabel>: <guilabel>Permission</guilabel> "
"column shows octal numbers '<literal>0755</literal>' instead of "
"'<literal>rwxr-xr-x</literal>'."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Številska dovoljenja</guilabel>: stolpec <guilabel>Dovoljenje</"
"guilabel> prikazuje osmiška števila '<literal>0755</literal>' namesto "
"'<literal>rwxr-xr-x</literal>'."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show hidden files</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays the "
"<quote>dot-files</quote> which are otherwise hidden."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži skrite datoteke</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; "
"prikaže <quote>dot-datoteke</quote>, ki so sicer skrite."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Load the user defined folder icons</guilabel>: If checked, "
"&krusader; loads the user defined folder icons."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Naloži ikone uporabniško določene mape</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"&krusader; naloži uporabniško določene ikone map."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Always show current item</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; shows "
"current item border decoration in inactive panel."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vedno prikaži trenutni element</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"&krusader; prikazuje trenutni okras obrobe elementa v neaktivni plošči."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sort method"
msgstr "Metoda razvrščanja"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Krusader (default)</guilabel>: the comparison used so far. Uses "
"comparison using locale rules (even context rules)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Krusader (privzeto)</guilabel>: doslej uporabljena primerjava. "
"Uporablja primerjavo z uporabo področnih pravil (celo kontekstnih pravil)."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Alphabetical</guilabel>: strings are compared character by "
"character (no context rules from locale applied). Alphabet characters are "
"compared using locale rules, special characters are compared by the "
"character code."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Abecedno</guilabel>: nizi se primerjajo znak za znakom "
"(uporabljajo se pravila konteksta iz področnih nastavitev). Abecedni znaki "
"se primerjajo z uporabo področnih pravil, posebni znaki se primerjajo s kodo "
"znakov."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Alphabetical and numbers</guilabel>: the same as above, but if the "
"names contains numbers, the numbers are compared numerically instead of "
"alphabetically."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Abeceda in številke</guilabel>: enako kot zgoraj, vendar če imena "
"vsebujejo številke, se številke primerjajo številčno namesto po abecedi."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Character code</guilabel>: comparison by character code (quick)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Znakovna koda</guilabel>: primerjava po znakovni kodi (hitra)."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Character code and numbers</guilabel>: the same as above, but with "
"numerical comparison of numbers."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Znakovna koda in številke</guilabel>: enako kot zgoraj, vendar z "
"numerično primerjavo števil."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case sensitive sorting</guilabel>: If checked (the &UNIX; "
"default), all files beginning with capital letters appear before files "
"beginning with non-capital letters; otherwise, all files beginning with a "
"specified letter (capital or otherwise) appear together."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razvrščanje z upoštevanjem velikih in malih črk</guilabel>: Če je "
"označeno (privzeto &UNIX;), se vse datoteke, ki se začnejo z velikimi "
"črkami, prikažejo pred datotekami, ki se začnejo z majhnimi črkami; sicer se "
"vse datoteke, ki se začnejo z določeno črko (veliko ali drugo), prikažejo "
"skupaj."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Always sort dirs by name</guilabel>: Sorts folders by name, "
"regardless of the sort column."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vedno razvrsti imenike po imenu</guilabel>: Razvrsti mape po "
"imenu, ne glede na stolpec za razvrščanje."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show folders first</guilabel>: If checked folders have precedence "
"in folder lists."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Najprej pokaži mape</guilabel>: Če je označeno, imajo mape "
"prednost na seznamih map."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Locale aware sorting</guilabel>: Sorts files and folders according "
"to the current locale settings."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razvrščanje glede na jezikovne nastavitve</guilabel>: Razvrsti "
"datoteke in mape glede na trenutne lokalne nastavitve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "View modes"
msgstr "Načini pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default view mode</guilabel>: Allows you to change the default "
"view mode. You can choose <guimenuitem>Detailed View</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Brief View</guimenuitem>. On tabs of both view modes you can "
"define the following options."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeti način pogleda</guilabel>: Omogoča spreminjanje privzetega "
"načina pogleda. Izberete lahko <guimenuitem>Podroben pogled</guimenuitem> "
"ali <guimenuitem>Kratek pogled</guimenuitem>. Na zavihkih obeh načinov "
"pogleda lahko določite naslednje možnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default icon size</guilabel>: Allows you to change the size of the "
"icons in the file lists. The available sizes are 12x12, 16x16, 22x22, 32x32, "
"48x48, 64x64, 128x128 and 256x256 pixels."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeta velikost ikon</guilabel>: Omogoča spreminjanje velikosti "
"ikon na seznamih datotek. Razpoložljive velikosti so 12x12, 16x16, 22x22, "
"32x32, 48x48, 64x64, 128x128 in 256x256 slikovnih pik."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use icons in the filenames</guilabel>: If checked, show the icons "
"in file names and folders."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabi ikone v imenih datotek</guilabel>: Če je označeno, prikaže "
"ikone v imenih datotek in map."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show previews by default</guilabel>: If checked, show the previews "
"of file contents."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeto pokaži predogled</guilabel>: Če je označeno, pokaži "
"predogled vsebine datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure the columns use the right click menu in the panel when viewing "
"files. The left and right panel use their own columns independently. The "
"following columns are available:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati stolpce, med ogledovanjem datotek uporabite meni z "
"desnim klikom na plošči. Leva in desna plošča neodvisno uporabljata svoje "
"stolpce. Na voljo so naslednji stolpci:"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Name</guilabel>: Shows the filename without the part after the "
"last dot, this latter part is displayed in the <guilabel>Ext</guilabel> "
"column. When the <guilabel>Ext</guilabel> column is made hidden, the "
"complete filename is shown in the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> column like &eg; "
"&konqueror; does."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel>: Prikaže ime datoteke brez dela za zadnjo piko, ta "
"zadnji del je prikazan v stolpcu <guilabel>Ext</guilabel>. Ko je stolpec "
"<guilabel>Ext</guilabel> skrit, je celotno ime datoteke prikazano v stolpcu "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, kot je &eg; &konqueror; počne."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Ext</guilabel>: Shows the last part of the filename (the part "
"after the last dot) in the <guilabel>Ext</guilabel> column, and not as a "
"complete filename in the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> column like &eg; "
"&konqueror; does."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ext</guilabel>: prikaže zadnji del imena datoteke (del za zadnjo "
"piko) v stolpcu <guilabel>Ext</guilabel> in ne kot celotno ime datoteke v "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel> stolpec kot &eg; &konqueror; počne."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Type</guilabel>: Shows the &MIME; type field."
msgstr "<guilabel>Vrsta</guilabel>: prikaže &MIME; tipsko polje."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Size</guilabel>: Shows the size field."
msgstr "<guilabel>Velikost</guilabel>: prikaže polje velikosti."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Modified</guilabel>: Shows the modified date and time field."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Spremenjeno</guilabel>: prikaže spremenjeno polje datuma in ure."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Perms</guilabel>: Shows the full permissions, &eg;, '<literal>rwxr-"
"xr-x</literal>' or as octal numbers '<literal>0755</literal>' instead with "
"enable/disable <guilabel>Numeric Permissions</guilabel> in <guilabel>Panel "
"View</guilabel> Tab."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Perms</guilabel>: prikaže polna dovoljenja, &eg;, '<literal>rwxr-"
"xr-x</literal>' ali kot osmiška števila '<literal>0755</literal>' namesto z "
"omogoči/onemogoči <guilabel>Številska dovoljenja</guilabel> v zavihku "
"<guilabel>Pogled plošče</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>rwx</guilabel>: Shows only the rights of the current user, &eg;, "
"<quote>-rw</quote>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>rwx</guilabel>: Prikazuje samo pravice trenutnega uporabnika, "
"&eg;, <quote>-rw</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Owner</guilabel>: Shows the owner field."
msgstr "<guilabel>Lastnik</guilabel>: prikaže polje lastnika."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Group</guilabel>: Shows the group field."
msgstr "<guilabel>Skupina</guilabel>: prikaže skupinsko polje."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uncheck the columns not in use. This allows more space for columns in use."
msgstr ""
"Odkljukajte stolpce, ki niso v uporabi. To omogoča več prostora za stolpce v "
"uporabi."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Toolbar buttons have icons</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; "
"displays icons on toolbar buttons."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Gumbi orodne vrstice imajo ikone</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"&krusader; prikaže ikone na gumbih orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show Media Button</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays "
"media button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži gumb za medije</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; "
"prikaže medijski gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show Back Button</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays back "
"button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži gumb Nazaj</guilabel>: Če je označeno, &krusader; prikaže "
"gumb za nazaj."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show Forward Button</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays "
"forward button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži gumb Naprej</guilabel>: Če je označeno, &krusader; prikaže "
"gumb naprej."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show History Button</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays "
"history button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Gumb za prikaz zgodovine</guilabel>: Če je označeno, &krusader; "
"prikaže gumb za zgodovino."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show Bookmarks Button</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays "
"bookmarks button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži gumb za zaznamke</guilabel>: Če je označeno, &krusader; "
"prikaže gumb za zaznamke."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show Panel Toolbar</guilabel>: If checked, &krusader; displays the "
"Panel Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži orodno vrstico plošče</guilabel>: če je označeno, "
"&krusader; prikaže orodno vrstico plošče."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make the buttons on the <guilabel>Panel Toolbar</guilabel> visible "
"or hidden:"
msgstr ""
"Gumbe v <guilabel>orodni vrstici plošče</guilabel> lahko naredite vidne ali "
"skrite:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Visible Panel Toolbar buttons"
msgstr "Vidni gumbi orodne vrstice plošče"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid "Equal button (=)"
msgstr "Gumb za enako (=)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Up button (..)"
msgstr "Gumb gor (..)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home button (~)"
msgstr "Gumb Domov (~)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Root button (/)"
msgstr "Korenski gumb (/)"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Toggle-button for sync-browsing</guilabel>: If checked, shows the "
"<link linkend=\"panel_toolbar\">Sync-browsing</link> button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preklopni gumb za sinhronizirano brskanje</guilabel>: Če je "
"označeno, prikaže gumb <link linkend=\"panel_toolbar\">Sinhronizirano "
"brskanje</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selection Mode"
msgstr "Način izbire"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can configure the selection modes."
msgstr "Tukaj lahko konfigurirate izbirne načine."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>&krusader; Mode</guilabel>: The way &krusader; has worked from day "
"one. Both mouse keys allow selecting files. To select more than one file, "
"hold the &Ctrl; key and click the &LMB;. Right-click menu appears with a "
"short click on the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>&krusader; Način</guilabel>: način &krusader; je delal od prvega "
"dne. Obe tipki miške omogočata izbiranje datotek. Če želite izbrati več kot "
"eno datoteko, držite &Ctrl; in kliknite &LMB;. Prikaže se meni z desnim "
"klikom s kratkim klikom na &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>&konqueror; Mode</guilabel>: pressing the &LMB; selects files -- "
"you can click and select multiple files. Right-click menu appears with a "
"short click on the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>&konqueror; Način</guilabel>: pritisk &LMB; izbere datoteke -- "
"lahko kliknete in izberete več datotek. Prikaže se meni z desnim klikom s "
"kratkim klikom na &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Total commander Mode</guilabel>: Pressing the &RMB; selects "
"multiple files and the right-click menu appears with <guilabel>pressing and "
"holding</guilabel> the &RMB;. The &LMB; does not select, but sets the "
"current file without affecting the current selection."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Način Total Commander</guilabel>: s pritiskom &RMB; izbere več "
"datotek in prikaže se meni z desnim klikom s <guilabel>pritiskom in "
"držanjem</guilabel> &RMB;. &LMB; ne izbere, ampak nastavi trenutno datoteko "
"brez vpliva na trenutno izbiro."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Ergonomic Mode</guilabel>: The &LMB; does not select, but sets the "
"current file without affecting the current selection. The &RMB; invokes the "
"context-menu. You can select with &Ctrl; key and the left button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ergonomski način</guilabel>: &LMB; ne izbere, ampak nastavi "
"trenutno datoteko brez vpliva na trenutno izbiro. &RMB; prikliče kontekstni "
"meni. Izberete lahko s tipko &Ctrl; tipko in levi gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Custom Selection Mode</guilabel>: Create your own selection style!"
msgstr "<guilabel>Način izbire po meri</guilabel>: Ustvarite svoj slog izbire!"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Double-click selects (classic)</guilabel>: A single click on a "
"file will select and focus, a double click opens the file or steps into the "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dvojni klik izbere (klasično)</guilabel>: En sam klik na datoteko "
"bo izbral in usmeril, dvojni klik pa odpre datoteko ali stopi v mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Obey global selection policy</guilabel>: Pressing the &LMB; "
"selects files -- Use global setting: <menuchoice><guimenu>Input Devices</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mouse </guimenuitem></menuchoice> module in the "
"&plasma; &systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Upoštevajte globalno politiko izbire</guilabel>: s pritiskom &LMB; "
"izbere datoteke -- Uporabi globalno nastavitev: <menuchoice><guimenu>Vhodne "
"naprave</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Miška </guimenuitem></menuchoice> modul v "
"&plasma; &systemsettings;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Selection Mode items:"
msgstr "Elementi načina izbire po meri:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Based on &plasma;'s selection mode"
msgstr "Na podlagi izbirnega &plasma; načina"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid "&LMB; selects"
msgstr "&LMB; izbira"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid "&LMB; preserves selection"
msgstr "&LMB; ohranja izbor"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;/&Ctrl; + left clicking selects"
msgstr "&Shift;/&Ctrl; + levi klik izbere"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid "&RMB; selects"
msgstr "&RMB; izbira"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid "&RMB; preserves selection"
msgstr "&RMB; ohranja izbor"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;/&Ctrl; + right clicking selects"
msgstr "&Shift;/&Ctrl; + desni klik izbere"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spacebar moves down"
msgstr "Preslednica se premakne navzdol"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert moves down"
msgstr "Vložek se premakne navzdol"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right-clicking pops context menu immediately"
msgstr "Z desnim klikom se takoj pojavi kontekstni meni"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>A plain mouse button resets selection</guilabel> - resets "
"selection on a mouse click without modifiers (&ie; &Shift; or &Ctrl;). "
"Selection with &Shift;/&Ctrl; for the mouse button has to be enabled for "
"this setting to work."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Navaden gumb miške ponastavi izbor</guilabel> - ponastavi izbor ob "
"kliku miške brez modifikatorjev (&ie; &Shift; ali &Ctrl;). Izbor s &Shift;/"
"&Ctrl; za gumb miške mora biti omogočen, da ta nastavitev deluje."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "Media Menu"
msgstr "Meni Mediji"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using this tab you can select the <link linkend=\"media_button\">Media "
"button</link> menu contents:"
msgstr ""
"S tem zavihkom lahko izberete vsebino menija <link linkend=\"media_button"
"\">gumba za medije</link>:"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show Mount Path</guilabel>: show the mount path of partition if "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži pot priklopa</guilabel>: prikaži pot priklopa particije, "
"če je označeno."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show File System Type</guilabel>: show the file system type of "
"partition if checked."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži vrsto datotečnega sistema</guilabel>: prikaži vrsto "
"datotečnega sistema particije, če je označeno."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide SquashFS entries</guilabel>: <ulink url=\"https://snapcraft."
"io/\">Snap</ulink> creates many <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"SquashFS\">SquashFS</ulink>-mounted partitions, which are almost useless in "
"the <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Media Menu</link>, because "
"<application>snap</application> manages them. It is possible to hide "
"SquashFS mounts by checking this item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skrij vnose SquashFS</guilabel>: <ulink url=\"https://snapcraft.io/"
"\">Snap</ulink> ustvari veliko <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ "
"SquashFS\">SquashFS</ulink> nameščene particije, ki so skoraj neuporabne v "
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">medijskem meniju</link>, ker jih upravlja "
"<application>snap</application>. Možno je skriti namestitve SquashFS, če "
"označite ta element."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide unknown File System entries</guilabel>: Several unknown File "
"System entries may appear in the <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Media Menu</"
"link>, which are almost useless there. It is possible to hide unknown File "
"System entries by checking this item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skrij neznane vnose v datotečni sistem</guilabel>: V <link linkend="
"\"list_panel\">meniju Predstavnost</link> se lahko prikaže več neznanih "
"vnosov v datotečni sistem, ki so tam skoraj neuporabni. Neznane vnose v "
"datotečni sistem je mogoče skriti tako, da označite to možnost."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide following mountpoints</guilabel>: this list allows to exclude "
"unwanted items from <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Media Menu</link>. Press "
"the <guibutton>+</guibutton> button above the list to add some mount point "
"you want to ignore. Should you decide to remove the added mount point from "
"the list just click on it and press the <guibutton>-</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skrij naslednje točke priklopa</guilabel>: ta seznam omogoča "
"izključitev neželenih elementov iz <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Medija "
"medijev</link>. Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>+</guibutton> nad seznamom, da "
"dodate točko priklopa, ki jo želite prezreti. Če se odločite odstraniti "
"dodano točko priklopa s seznama, jo kliknite in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>-"
"</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show Size:</guilabel> allows selection of the size representation "
"in media menu. Can be <guimenuitem>Always</guimenuitem> (default, always "
"show the size of partition), <guimenuitem>When Device has no Label</"
"guimenuitem> (show the size for partitions with no label only) or "
"<guimenuitem>Never</guimenuitem> (never show the size in media menu)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži velikost:</guilabel> omogoča izbiro predstavitve velikosti "
"v medijskem meniju. Lahko <guimenuitem>Vedno</guimenuitem> (privzeto, vedno "
"prikaže velikost particije), <guimenuitem>Ko naprava nima oznake</"
"guimenuitem> (prikaže velikost samo za particije brez oznake) ali "
"<guimenuitem>Nikoli</guimenuitem> (nikoli ne pokaži velikosti v meniju "
"medijev)."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid "Layout"
msgstr "Postavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:772
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose the layout and frame settings:"
msgstr "Izberete lahko nastavitve postavitve in okvirja:"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Layout:</guilabel> allows to define layout. The default options "
"are <guimenuitem>Default</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Compact</guimenuitem>, "
"and <guimenuitem>Classic</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Postavitev:</guilabel> omogoča določitev postavitve. Privzete "
"možnosti so <guimenuitem>Privzeto</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Kompaktno</"
"guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Klasično</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Frame Color:</guilabel> defines frame color. Can be "
"<guimenuitem>Defined by Layout</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>None</"
"guimenuitem>, or <guimenuitem>Statusbar</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Barva okvirja:</guilabel> določa barvo okvirja. Lahko "
"<guimenuitem>Določeno s postavitvijo</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Brez</"
"guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Statusna vrstica</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Frame Shape:</guilabel> defines frame color. Can be "
"<guimenuitem>Defined by Layout</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>None</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Box</guimenuitem>, or <guimenuitem>Panel</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Oblika okvirja:</guilabel> določa barvo okvirja. Lahko "
"<guimenuitem>Določeno s postavitvijo</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Brez</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Polje</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Plošče</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Frame Shadow:</guilabel> defines frame color. Can be "
"<guimenuitem>Defined by Layout</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>None</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Raised</guimenuitem>, or <guimenuitem>Sunken</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Senca okvirja:</guilabel> določa barvo okvirja. Lahko "
"<guimenuitem>Določeno s postavitvijo</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Brez</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Dvignjeno</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem>Potopljeno</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Colors</title>"
msgstr "<title>Barve</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page configures the colors of the <link linkend=\"list_panel\">List "
"Panel</link> and the <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer</link>. The "
"<guilabel>&kde; default colors</guilabel> is the default color configuration."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran konfigurira barve <link linkend=\"list_panel\">podokna s seznamom</"
"link> in <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">sinhronizatorja</link>. "
"<guilabel>&kde; privzete barve</guilabel>je privzeta barvna konfiguracija."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:809
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use the default &kde; colors</guilabel>: this is the default, it "
"uses &plasma; color defined in the &systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabi privzeti &kde; barve</guilabel>: to je privzeto, uporablja "
"&plasma; barva, določena v &systemsettings;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use Alternate Background color</guilabel>: If checked, the "
"<guilabel>Background</guilabel> color and the <guilabel>Alternate "
"background</guilabel> color alternates line by line. When you do not use the "
"&plasma; default colors, you can configure the alternate colors in the "
"<guilabel>Colors</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabi nadomestno barvo ozadja</guilabel>: če je označeno, se "
"barva <guilabel>ozadja</guilabel> in barva <guilabel>nadomestnega ozadja</"
"guilabel> izmenjujeta vrstico za vrstico. Ko ne uporabljate &plasma; "
"privzete barve, lahko konfigurirate nadomestne barve v polju "
"<guilabel>Barve</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show current item even if not focused</guilabel>: If checked, "
"shows the last cursor position in the non active list panel. This option is "
"only available when you do not use the &plasma; default colors."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaži trenutni element, tudi če ni fokusiran</guilabel>: Če je "
"označeno, prikaže zadnji položaj kazalca na plošči neaktivnega seznama. Ta "
"možnost je na voljo le, če ne uporabljate &plasma; privzete barve."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Dim the colors of the inactive panel</guilabel>: If checked, the "
"colors of the inactive panel are dimmed. These settings can be configured in "
"the <guilabel>Inactive</guilabel> tab of the <guilabel>Colors</guilabel> "
"box. This option is only available when you do not use the &plasma; default "
"colors."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zatemni barve neaktivne plošče</guilabel>: Če je označeno, so "
"barve neaktivne plošče zatemnjene. Te nastavitve lahko konfigurirate na "
"zavihku <guilabel>Neaktivno</guilabel> polja <guilabel>Barve</guilabel>. Ta "
"možnost je na voljo le, če ne uporabljate &plasma; privzete barve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:849
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Colors</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Barve</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:852
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure the colors the way you like, you can see the result in the "
"<guilabel>Preview</guilabel> section. The following items of the active and "
"inactive panel can be configured:"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte barve, kot želite, rezultat si lahko ogledate v razdelku "
"<guilabel>Predogled</guilabel>. Konfigurirate lahko naslednje elemente "
"aktivne in neaktivne plošče:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid "Foreground"
msgstr "Ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder foreground"
msgstr "Ospredje mape"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid "Executable foreground"
msgstr "Izvedljivo ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid "Symbolic link foreground"
msgstr "Simbolična povezava v ospredju"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invalid symlink foreground"
msgstr "Ospredje neveljavne simbolne povezave"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background"
msgstr "Ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:890
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alternate background"
msgstr "Nadomestno ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:895
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selected foreground"
msgstr "Izbrano ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selected background"
msgstr "Izbrano ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:905
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alternate selected background"
msgstr "Nadomestno izbrano ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:910
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current foreground"
msgstr "Trenutno ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selected current foreground"
msgstr "Izbrano trenutno ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current background"
msgstr "Trenutno ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:925
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename foreground"
msgstr "Preimenuj ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename background"
msgstr "Preimenuj ozadje"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following items of the <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer</"
"link> can be configured:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednje elemente <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizerja</link> je "
"mogoče konfigurirati:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid "Equals foreground"
msgstr "Enako ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:944
#, no-c-format
msgid "Equals background"
msgstr "Enako ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid "Differing foreground"
msgstr "Različno ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid "Differing background"
msgstr "Različno ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy to left foreground"
msgstr "Kopiraj v levo ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:964 konfigurator.docbook:974
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy to left background"
msgstr "Kopiraj v levo ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy to right foreground"
msgstr "Kopiraj v desno ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete foreground"
msgstr "Izbriši ospredje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete background"
msgstr "Izbriši ozadje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:992
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Predogled"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you see a preview of the configured colors."
msgstr "Tukaj vidite predogled konfiguriranih barv."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color schemes"
msgstr "Barvne sheme"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guibutton>Import Color Scheme</guibutton> and <guibutton>Export "
"Color Scheme</guibutton> buttons you can load and save a Color Scheme "
"profile. This allows &krusader; to use <trademark class=\"copyright\">Total "
"Commander</trademark>, <application>Midnight Commander</application>, foo-"
"commander or your own custom color profile. The Color Schemes are stored in "
"<filename>/usr/share/krusader</filename>, the <filename>foo.color</filename> "
"is a binary file that holds the color scheme."
msgstr ""
"Z gumboma <guibutton>Uvozi barvno shemo</guibutton> in <guibutton>Izvozi "
"barvno shemo</guibutton> lahko naložite in shranite profil barvne sheme. To "
"omogoča &krusader; za uporabo <trademark class=\"copyright\">Total "
"Commander</trademark>, <application>Midnight Commander</application>, foo-"
"commander ali lastnega barvnega profila po meri. Barvne sheme so shranjene v "
"<filename>/usr/share/krusader</filename>, <filename>foo.color</filename> je "
"binarna datoteka, ki vsebuje barvno shemo."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>Midnight Commander</application> and <trademark class="
"\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark> Color scheme files are provided. "
"Please <link linkend=\"help_krusader\">upload your favorite Color schemes</"
"link> so that they become available for the &krusader; community. Thanks!"
msgstr ""
"Na voljo sta datoteki barvne sheme <application>Midnight Commander</"
"application> in <trademark class=\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark>. "
"<link linkend=\"help_krusader\">Naložite svoje najljubše barvne sheme</"
"link>, da bodo na voljo za &krusader; skupnosti. Hvala!"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you configure the basic operations. The page is divided into three "
"tabs: <guilabel>General</guilabel>, <guilabel>Viewer/Editor</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Atomic extensions</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj konfigurirate osnovne operacije. Stran je razdeljena na tri zavihke: "
"<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>, <guilabel>Pregledovalnik/urejevalnik</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Atomic razširitve</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following options determine basic aspects of operation:"
msgstr "Naslednje možnosti določajo osnovne vidike delovanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Warn on exit</guilabel>: if checked, &krusader; warns you every "
"time when exit action is triggered."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Opozori ob izhodu</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; vas "
"opozori vsakič, ko se sproži izhod."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show and close to tray</guilabel>: If checked, the &krusader; icon "
"will appear in the system tray. When you minimize &krusader;, it will not "
"appear in the taskbar. It also will not exit if you close the main window. "
"Instead you can quit &krusader; by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or the "
"context menu of the tray icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži in zapri pladenj</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; "
"ikona se prikaže v sistemski vrstici. Ko minimizirate &krusader;, ne bo "
"prikazan v opravilni vrstici. Prav tako se ne bo zaprl, če zaprete glavno "
"okno. Namesto tega lahko zaprete &krusader; tako, da izberete menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali kontekstni meni ikone v pladnju."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use &MIME; type magic</guilabel>: &MIME; type magic is a mechanism "
"which allows &krusader; to inspect the files in the panels and determine "
"their type even if the file has no identifying extension. For example, if "
"you take an image file - <filename>image1.jpg</filename> - and rename it to "
"<filename>image1</filename>, &krusader; will still know it is an image file "
"and work with it accordingly. However, this mode of operation is slower "
"(while refreshing the panel, or changing folders), so try &krusader; with "
"and without &MIME; type magic and decide what is best for you."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabi &MIME; tip magic</guilabel>: &MIME; type magic je "
"mehanizem, ki omogoča &krusader; da pregledate datoteke v panelih in "
"določite njihovo vrsto, tudi če datoteka nima identifikacijske pripone. Če "
"na primer vzamete slikovno datoteko - <filename>image1.jpg</filename> - in "
"jo preimenujete v <filename>image1</filename>, &krusader; bo še vedno vedel, "
"da je slikovna datoteka, in z njo ustrezno delal. Vendar je ta način "
"delovanja počasnejši (med osveževanjem plošče ali spreminjanjem map), zato "
"poskusite &krusader; z in brez &MIME; vnesite magijo in se odločite, kaj je "
"za vas najboljše."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Temp Folder</guilabel>: this option selects the base folder for "
"&krusader;'s temporary files. The actual files will be created in separate "
"folders under the 'Temp folder', so that each user running &krusader; will "
"have their own temporary subfolders under the chosen folder."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Začasna mapa</guilabel>: ta možnost izbere osnovno mapo za začasne "
"datoteke &krusader;. Dejanske datoteke bodo ustvarjene v ločenih mapah v "
"'Začasni mapi', tako da bo vsak uporabnik, ki zažene &krusader; bodo imeli "
"svoje začasne podmape v izbrani mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You must choose a temporary folder to which all users running &krusader; "
"have full permissions!"
msgstr ""
"Izbrati morate začasno mapo, v katero bodo vsi uporabniki, ki izvajajo "
"&krusader; imeti polna dovoljenja!"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Delete mode</guilabel> (<guilabel>Delete files/Move to trash</"
"guilabel>): when &krusader; deletes files it can either <emphasis>really</"
"emphasis> delete them or move them to the trash folder, thereby making them "
"available via &plasma;'s trash."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Način brisanja</guilabel> (<guilabel>Brisanje datotek/premakni v "
"koš</guilabel>): ko &krusader; izbriše datoteke, jih lahko <emphasis>res</"
"emphasis> izbriše ali premakne v mapo smetnjak, s čimer postanejo na voljo "
"prek smetnjaka &plasma;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>External Terminal</guilabel>: choose which terminal emulator will "
"be used when &krusader; opens a console window (via <keycap>F9</keycap>, or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Start Terminal</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu option)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zunanji terminal</guilabel>: izberite, kateri terminalski emulator "
"bo uporabljen, ko &krusader; odpre okno konzole (prek <keycap>F9</keycap> "
"ali menijske možnosti <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zaženi terminal</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Embedded Terminal sends Chdir on panel change</guilabel>: if "
"unchecked, there will be no <command>cd</command> command sent to the "
"Terminal Emulator if the panel folder changes."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vdelani terminal pošlje Chdir ob spremembi plošče</guilabel>: če "
"ni označeno, ukaz <command>cd</command> ne bo poslan terminalskemu "
"emulatorju, če se spremeni mapa plošče."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Active panel follows Embedded Terminal working directory</"
"guilabel>: if unchecked, active panel stays unchanged while the user "
"navigates in the embedded terminal (using cd, popd, etc)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Aktivna plošča sledi delovnemu imeniku vdelanega terminala</"
"guilabel>: če ni označena, ostane aktivna plošča nespremenjena, medtem ko se "
"uporabnik pomika po vdelanem terminalu (z uporabo cd, popd itd.)."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Toggle Fullscreen Embedded Terminal</guilabel>: if checked, "
"&krusader; shows fullscreen terminal in <application>Midnight Commander</"
"application> style (Terminal is shown instead of &krusader; window)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preklopi celozaslonski vgrajeni terminal</guilabel>: če je "
"označeno, &krusader; prikazuje celozaslonski terminal v slogu "
"<application>Midnight Commander</application> (Terminal je prikazan namesto "
"okna &krusader;)."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewer/Editor"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik/urejevalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can change the viewer and editor settings:"
msgstr "Tukaj lahko spremenite nastavitve pregledovalnika in urejevalnika:"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Internal editor and viewer opens each file in separate window</"
"guilabel>: check this item if you want each file to be opened in a separate "
"window. If unchecked, each file will be opened in a tab in the same Viewer/"
"Editor window. Every tab in such a window can be closed, among other common "
"methods, by clicking on the tab with the &MMB;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Notranji urejevalnik in pregledovalnik odpre vsako datoteko v "
"ločenem oknu</guilabel>: označite ta element, če želite, da se vsaka "
"datoteka odpre v ločenem oknu. Če ni označeno, bo vsaka datoteka odprta na "
"zavihku v istem oknu pregledovalnika/urejevalnika. Vsak zavihek v takem oknu "
"je med drugimi običajnimi metodami mogoče zapreti s klikom na zavihek z "
"&MMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Hide the tab bar when only one tab is opened</guilabel>: check "
"this item if you want the Viewer/Editor tab bar to be hidden if only one tab "
"is open."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skrij vrstico z zavihki, ko je odprt samo en zavihek</guilabel>: "
"označite to postavko, če želite, da je vrstica z zavihki Pregledovalnik/"
"Urejevalnik skrita, če je odprt samo en zavihek."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Default viewer mode</guilabel>:"
msgstr "<guilabel>Privzeti način pregledovalnika</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Generic mode</guilabel>: use the systems default viewer."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Generični način</guilabel>: uporabite sistemski privzeti "
"pregledovalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Text mode</guilabel>: view the file in text-only mode."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Besedilni način</guilabel>: oglejte si datoteko samo v besedilnem "
"načinu."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Hex mode</guilabel>: view the file in hex-only mode."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Šestnajstiški način</guilabel>: ogled datoteke samo v "
"šestnajstiškem načinu."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Lister mode</guilabel>: Fast text/hexadecimal viewer for huge "
"filesizes. &krusader; lister never loads the whole file into memory, just a "
"little part of it, and uses caching for faster scrolling. Remote files are "
"downloaded, but during the download, viewing the downloaded part is "
"possible. If a file constantly changes, then it can also be viewed, lister "
"will always see its current state."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Način seznama</guilabel>: Hiter besedilni/šestnajstiški "
"pregledovalnik za velike datoteke. &krusader; lister nikoli ne naloži "
"celotne datoteke v pomnilnik, le njen majhen del, in uporablja predpomnjenje "
"za hitrejše pomikanje. Prenesejo se oddaljene datoteke, vendar je med "
"prenosom možen ogled prenesenega dela. Če se datoteka nenehno spreminja, jo "
"je mogoče tudi pregledati, listalnik bo vedno videl njeno trenutno stanje."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use lister if the text file is bigger than: 10 MB (default value)</"
"guilabel>: checks whether a text file is bigger than 10 MB (configurable), "
"and if yes, then &krusader; Lister is used instead of &plasma;'s default "
"viewer."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabite lister, če je besedilna datoteka večja od: 10 MB "
"(privzeta vrednost)</guilabel>: preveri, ali je besedilna datoteka večja od "
"10 MB (nastavljivo), in če je, potem &krusader; Lister se uporablja namesto "
"privzetega pregledovalnika &plasma;."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use Okteta as Hex viewer</guilabel>: if checked, use &plasma; hex "
"editor <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/index.php?application=okteta"
"\">Okteta</ulink> to view raw data. To use this option you should install "
"<application>Okteta</application> package first."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uporabi Okteta kot šestnajstiški pregledovalnik</guilabel>: če je "
"odkljukano, uporabi &plasma; hex urejevalnik <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde."
"org/index.php?application=okteta\">Okteta</ulink> za ogled neobdelanih "
"podatkov. Za uporabo te možnosti morate najprej namestiti paket "
"<application>Okteta</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Editor</guilabel>: choose what editor will be used when editing a "
"file (via <keycap>F4</keycap>). Default the internal viewer is used, this is "
"the &plasma;'s default viewer."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Urejevalnik</guilabel>: izberite urejevalnik, ki bo uporabljen pri "
"urejanju datoteke (preko <keycap>F4</keycap>). Privzeto je uporabljen "
"notranji pregledovalnik, to je privzeti pregledovalnik &plasma;."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Atomic extensions"
msgstr "Atomske razširitve"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Atomic extensions</guilabel>: predefined atomic extensions like "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> are shown as one part in the "
"<guilabel>Ext</guilabel> Column of the <link linkend=\"list_panel\">List "
"Panel</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Atomske razširitve</guilabel>: vnaprej določene atomske "
"razširitve, kot je <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal>, so "
"prikazane kot en del v stolpcu <guilabel>Ext</guilabel> v <link linkend="
"\"list_panel\">Plošča s seznamom</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:1183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Napredno"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page handles more advanced issues, so you should double-check your "
"actions here: modifying settings here <emphasis>makes &krusader; a more "
"powerful and dangerous tool.</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"Ta stran obravnava zahtevnejša vprašanja, zato bi morali še enkrat preveriti "
"svoja dejanja tukaj: spreminjanje nastavitev tukaj <emphasis>naredi "
"&krusader; močnejše in nevarnejše orodje.</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1189
#, no-c-format
msgid "The page is divided into three parts:"
msgstr "Stran je razdeljena na tri dele:"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Automount filesystems</guilabel>: this makes &krusader; try to "
"mount a file system before entering it. For example, if you click on "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/mnt/cdrom</filename> (and <filename class="
"\"directory\"> /mnt/cdrom</filename> appears in <filename class=\"directory"
"\">/etc/fstab</filename> as a mount point), &krusader; will check if it is "
"mounted. If not, it will try and mount it for you and then enter, so that "
"you would see the contents of your &CD-ROM;. Note, however, that &krusader; "
"will NOT unmount when exiting <filename class=\"directory\"> /mnt/cdrom</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samodejno priklopi datotečne sisteme</guilabel>: s tem &krusader; "
"poskusite namestiti datotečni sistem, preden vstopite vanj. Na primer, če "
"kliknete <filename class=\"directory\">/mnt/cdrom</filename> (in se "
"<filename class=\"directory\"> /mnt/cdrom</filename> prikaže v <filename "
"class=\"directory\" >/etc/fstab</filename> kot točka priklopa), &krusader; "
"bo preveril, če je nameščen. Če ne, ga bo poskusil namestiti namesto vas in "
"nato vstopil, da boste videli vsebino vašega &CD-ROM;a. Upoštevajte pa, da "
"&krusader; NE bo odklopljen, ko zapustite <filename class=\"directory\"> /"
"mnt/cdrom</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>MountMan will not (un)mount the following mount points</guilabel>: "
"If you have file systems that you do not want to accidentally unmount (or "
"mount) then enter a list of mount points separated by commas (&eg; "
"<literal>/, /boot, /tmp</literal>) and <link linkend=\"mount-man\">MountMan</"
"link> will not try to (un)mount them."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>MountMan ne bo (od)priklopil naslednjih točk priklopa</guilabel>: "
"Če imate datotečne sisteme, ki jih ne želite pomotoma odklopiti (ali "
"priklopiti), vnesite seznam točk priklopa, ločenih z vejicami (&eg; "
"<literal>/, /boot, /tmp</literal>) in <link linkend=\"mount-man\">MountMan</"
"link> jih ne bo poskušal (od)vklopiti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Confirmations"
msgstr "Potrditve"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By checking the options in this section, &krusader; will ask for "
"confirmation before doing a specific action; otherwise, the following "
"actions will be done without warning:"
msgstr ""
"Če preverite možnosti v tem razdelku, &krusader; bo prosil za potrditev, "
"preden izvede določeno dejanje; sicer bodo naslednja dejanja izvedena brez "
"opozorila:"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting non-empty folders"
msgstr "Brisanje nepraznih map"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting files"
msgstr "Brisanje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copying files"
msgstr "Kopiranje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving files"
msgstr "Premikanje datotek"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:1275 konfigurator.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fine-Tuning"
msgstr "Natančna nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Icon cache size (KB)</guilabel>: &krusader; uses an icon cache, so "
"it will not have to reload icons that have been used before. Of course, as "
"the cache grows bigger, it can store more icons and further speed "
"operations, but the memory footprint of &krusader; will become bigger."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Velikost predpomnilnika ikon (KB)</guilabel>: &krusader; uporablja "
"predpomnilnik ikon, tako da mu ne bo treba znova naložiti ikon, ki so bile "
"uporabljene prej. Seveda, ko se predpomnilnik poveča, lahko shrani več ikon "
"in pospeši operacije, toda pomnilniški odtis &krusader; bo postal večji."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Arguments of updatedb</guilabel>: sets additional arguments for "
"<command>updatedb</command>, please read the manpages for more information."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Argumenti za updatedb</guilabel>: nastavi dodatne argumente za "
"<command>updatedb</command>, za več informacij preberite man strani."

#. Tag: title
#: konfigurator.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archives"
msgstr "Arhivi"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1303
#, no-c-format
msgid "This page configures some aspects of archive handling in &krusader;."
msgstr "Ta stran konfigurira nekatere vidike rokovanja z arhivi v &krusader;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:1309
#, no-c-format
msgid "krarc ioslave"
msgstr "krarc ioslave"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Enable Write Support</guilabel>: this option allows you to enable "
"writing files into an archive."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Omogoči podporo za pisanje</guilabel>: ta možnost vam omogoča, da "
"omogočite pisanje datotek v arhiv."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The down side is that if a power failure occurs during the process, the "
"files that were moved might already be deleted, but not yet packed into the "
"archive. Moving archives into themselves will delete them."
msgstr ""
"Slaba stran je, da če med postopkom pride do izpada električne energije, so "
"premaknjene datoteke morda že izbrisane, vendar še niso zapakirane v arhiv. "
"Če arhive premaknete vase, jih boste izbrisali."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: konfigurator.docbook:1327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive handling"
msgstr "Arhivsko ravnanje"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Browse Archives As Folders</guilabel>: if checked, &krusader; will "
"handle the archives transparently and let you open them as folders; "
"otherwise, &krusader; will attempt to invoke an application which opens "
"archives of that type."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prebrskaj arhive kot mape</guilabel>: če je označeno, &krusader; "
"pregledno bo obravnaval arhive in vam omogočil, da jih odprete kot mape; "
"sicer pa &krusader; bo poskušal priklicati aplikacijo, ki odpira arhive te "
"vrste."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Test archive after packing</guilabel>: this option automatically "
"runs a test on a newly packed archive. It is safer, but takes longer."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preizkusi arhiv po pakiranju</guilabel>: ta možnost samodejno "
"zažene preizkus na novo zapakiranem arhivu. Je varnejše, a traja dlje."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Test archives before unpacking</guilabel>: this option "
"automatically runs a test before unpacking. Some corrupted archives might "
"cause a crash; therefore, it is better to test archives before unpacking."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preizkusi arhive pred razpakiranjem</guilabel>: ta možnost "
"samodejno zažene preizkus pred razpakiranjem. Nekateri poškodovani arhivi "
"lahko povzročijo zrušitev; zato je bolje, da arhive pred razpakiranjem "
"preizkusite."

