"lahko pa uporabite tudi svoj najljubši pripomoček za razlikovanje &eg; "
"<ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</application></"
"ulink> ali <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3 /"
"\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink>, samo vnesite celotno pot in "
"uživajte."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: konfigurator.docbook:1540
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packers tab"
msgstr "Pakirni zavihek"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Packers</guilabel> tab you will see a list of archive "
"formats. Some are filled and some are empty. The ones that are available "
"(filled) are supported by &krusader;. For them, &krusader; will handle the "
"archives transparently and let you open them as folders (provided you have "
"checked the <guilabel>Browse Archives As Folders</guilabel> item in the "
"<link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">Archives</link> section); otherwise, "
"&krusader; will attempt to invoke an application which opens archives of "
"that type. If a certain archive item is empty, it means that &krusader; "
"could not find the appropriate executables in the configured path. The next "
"archives are supported: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, lzma, rar, "
"rpm, tar, xz, zip and 7z."
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku <guilabel>Pakirniki</guilabel> boste videli seznam formatov "
"arhivov. Nekateri so napolnjeni, nekateri pa prazni. Tiste, ki so na voljo "
"(izpolnjene), podpira &krusader;. Zanje &krusader; bo transparentno "
"obravnaval arhive in vam omogočil, da jih odprete kot mape (pod pogojem, da "
"ste označili element <guilabel>Prebrskaj arhive kot mape</guilabel> v "
"razdelku <link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">Arhivi</link>); sicer pa "
"&krusader; bo poskušal priklicati aplikacijo, ki odpira arhive te vrste. Če "
"je določena arhivska postavka prazna, to pomeni, da &krusader; ni mogel "
"najti ustreznih izvršljivih datotek na konfigurirani poti. Podprti so "
"naslednji arhivi: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, lzma, rar, rpm, tar, "
"xz, zip in 7z."

